org.jemmy.control

Annotation Type As


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
@Documented
public @interface As
    This annotation should be used to annotate methods which turn a wrap into a control interface. It is, then, used in Wrap.as(*) and Wrap.is(*) methods and in *Dock.as*() methods.
    Author:
    shura
    See Also:
    Wrap.as(java.lang.Class), Wrap.as(java.lang.Class, java.lang.Class), Wrap.is(java.lang.Class), Wrap.is(java.lang.Class, java.lang.Class)
